{
    "text": "How does Twitter threading work?",
    "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:32:12 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "This came up in an email discussion. ",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:32:19 GMT"
        },
        {
            "text": "Doc said he doesn't really understand how Twitter threading works. I'm not sure I understand it either, and I've implemented it in two of my tools, first \"Electric Pork\" and now \"LO2\". ",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:35:58 GMT"
        },
        {
            "text": "Here's how I do it.",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:33:32 GMT"
        },
        {
            "text": "Suppose you have a sequence of four bits of text you want to turn into a Twitter thread.",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:33:37 GMT"
        },
        {
            "text": "Label them A, B, C and D. ",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:34:00 GMT"
        },
        {
            "text": "When you post a tweet you can optionally specify which tweet it is in reply to.",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:34:18 GMT"
        },
        {
            "text": "First I post A to Twitter, not a reply.",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:34:32 GMT",
            "subs": [
                {
                    "text": "Then I post B, in reply to A.",
                    "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:34:57 GMT",
                    "subs": [
                        {
                            "text": "Then C, in reply to B.",
                            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:35:08 GMT",
                            "subs": [
                                {
                                    "text": "And D, in reply to C.",
                                    "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:35:17 GMT"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "Twitter will display that as a thread. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1231425763284594689\">Like this</a>. ",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:34:10 GMT"
        },
        {
            "text": "Could I have had them all in reply to A? Not sure. I haven't tried it. ",
            "created": "Sun, 23 Feb 2020 03:35:32 GMT"
        }
    ]
}